window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nikolai: She came to my territory to spy on me. No one does that and lives. But this girl, she's a rare beauty. She's a temptation I have to conquer, and so I make her an offer. My mark, on her skin. The Volkov family insignia tattooed on her shoulder, to tell the world she's mine, and she earns my protection.</p> <p>It starts out as a game but becomes an obsession. Trouble is, I can't tell who is winning the game.</p> <p>Sienna: As a low-level street informant, I thought I'd finally gotten out and could resume my life, but I was mistaken. My handler had one last job for me. He wanted me to worm my way into the world of Nikolai Volkov, Slovakian arms dealer and a very bad person. The first day of working at his mysterious Club V, I knew I was in over my head. Powerful, beautiful, and full of charismatic energy, he enticed me and terrified me.</p> <p>So here I am. He says he will protect me, so long as I wear his mark and become his.</p> <p>At first, I try to tell myself I can play his twisted games, but as time goes on, he takes over my body, my heart, and now he wants my very soul.</p> <p>Nikolai Volkov is either going to be my downfall, or my savior, and I don't know which.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
